The CH340 driver can be downloaded from the following locations 

https://www.wch.cn/download/CH341SER_EXE.html   
Download the CH341SER.EXE file and run it to install the driver.

Alternatively the CH340 driver download 
https://learn.sparkfun.com/tutorials/how-to-install-ch340-drivers/all#drivers-if-you-need-them
